, ngokusho kwekhono. \n- {@green} Isithiyo{@DEFAULT}: Imelana nomonakalo olingana ne-HP ye-barrier. \n- {@green} Reflect{@DEFAULT}: Thola kuphela u-80% womonakalo ovela esitheni, bese ubuyisela u-20% kumhlaseli. \n- {@green} Amasosha omzimba{@DEFAULT}: Amasosha omzimba kuyo yonke imiphumela eyingozi. Imiphumela eyingozi yamanje ayisuswa. \n- {@green} HP Absorption{@DEFAULT}: Buyisa u-10% womonakalo owenziwe esitheni njenge-HP.',
